name: Captain Panaka
Lore: 'Leader of Amidala''s royal guard who personally supervised the Queen''s weapon and self-defense training. Served under Captain Magneta before his current assignment.',
Text: 'Deploys -1 to same site as Amidala. Once per game, may deploy a blaster on Panaka from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Once per turn, if Panaka just fired a blaster and ''hit'' a character, opponent loses 2 Force.',
